				\begin{document}$$ i=\mathit{\log}\frac{\%\left(\frac{serovar}{source}\right)}{\%\left(\frac{strains}{source}\right)} $$\end{document}i=log%serovarsource%strainssource) represent the common logarithm of the number of strains per source for each specific serovar (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
